Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:45.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:50.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次我想请大家去海水浴  附带温泉一宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去海边吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:04.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝仓君？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个能遮的住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人  您想买什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…小鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:58.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你喜欢这样的啊  朝仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太色了  朝仓纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:08.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被说中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要耍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:18.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉  完全被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:24.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这两年的后勤部队可不是白做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:32.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你全方位看了个够的这两年…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果考关于朝仓君的题目的话  我能得不错的分数哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能高过一般人不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:47.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和音梦约好了见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟你也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:54.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  去享受你们两个人的时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:56.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我向音梦问好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:07.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:12.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出局…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:16.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要“非常草莓”和“卷花焦糖”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买双份的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:19.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你迟到的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:20.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音梦你要什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:23.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:28.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  有个地方想和哥哥一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一个“薄荷之吻”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三份吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橡…橡皮艇(gomu booto)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:58.20,DefaultS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\an8}{\pos(352,10)}注释：[尻取り]（接龙）是将前一个日语单词的最后一个发音做为开始，由下一个人继续\N说一个词，以此类推。由于和中文发音不一样，看翻译后的中文是看不明白的，所以把每\N个日语的读音用罗马字写了出来，大家自己注意看下就明白了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橡皮艇的‘to’
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:55.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是‘to’吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:56.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是关于海的接龙游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要用和海有关的来接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:03.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“土用波”(doyounami)行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:03.23,DefaultS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\an8}{\pos(352,10)}注释：立秋前18天前后，由于台风而引起的洋面上的大浪。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mi… 泳衣(mizugi)！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mizugi的‘gi’？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:14.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gi… 只放卷心菜的炒面(yakisoba)！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:22.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\an8}{\pos(352,10)}注释：キャベツ（卷心菜）的第一个发音是“ki”，虽然不是“gi”，不过是“gi”的清\N　　　音。也算蒙混过去了。所以下边纯一说“还算OK”。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:20.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海之家的炒面  几乎不加什么料的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点夸张不过还算OK  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面轮到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是‘ba’啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:38.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ba…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每幢样子都不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇  有几幢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看  选对地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢  眼光不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ba…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  别想接龙的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:04.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香草冰激凌(baniraaisu)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子  下一个是‘su’哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‘su’啊…su…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早结束了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜(suika)啊！  西瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衫并！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临西洋风格小屋‘我的家’
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然先来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你怎么不来集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:29.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天很热吧  进来喝点冰豆浆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要自己装出一副主人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  不要计较这些小事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:39.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点换衣服去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里边是什么样的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我给朝仓你预备了特别房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好宽敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:54.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:58.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是烤鱼的烤炉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:02.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是Mantelpiece  是北欧的暖炉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:05.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是夏天  所以不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这个也可以拿来烤鱼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:15.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊  海好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:18.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们马上就可以去游泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:27.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这哪里是特别房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:35.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是能充分体验自然的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能净化被现代文明所污染的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是治疗的空间  恢复之所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很特别很高级吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真会说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱茜亚你的脸都红了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚  完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:11.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要穿上哥哥选的泳衣  还是有点害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的  肯定合适你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝仓君会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  这么慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:41.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想让哥哥第一个看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:42.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有这事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  没错  YES！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:05.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次穿的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱茜亚好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:22.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看  是用香蕉皮做的新材料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:47.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸合适的只有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:54.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是夏娃！ 这泳衣简直就是为了让水越姐穿而诞生的～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  这么说小鸟呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:43.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  切的好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿环好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:01.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是爱丽丝想吃的烤鱿鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:06.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像和想象中的大不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:12.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  做的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:16.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师  这个很有艺术感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:20.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一部作品是以这个城堡为舞台吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:21.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:23.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:28.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼  要是海水是甜的那就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:32.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱茜亚你知道为什么海水又咸又涩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:34.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:41.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为  伤心欲绝的少女的眼泪流到海里的缘故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少女的眼泪？  是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:48.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分诗情画意又很甜蜜的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故事？  这是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦？  老师  你开玩笑的本领也是一流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:12.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的贝壳啊  音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:19.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的泳衣  很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:21.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起拣贝壳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:25.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面我们玩计分的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很笨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来海边玩竟然会忘记泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得好好谢谢你  小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是这次聚会的主要目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:19.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我很多帮助  为我做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:21.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上叫醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:24.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烫衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:27.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有替我猜考题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:32.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  还有一次洗澡某人忘记给我烧热水了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:41.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两年尽是给小鸟你们添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:48.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟  好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:07.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很有趣  这两年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:21.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:25.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该去准备烧烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:26.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:27.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:41.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还…对朝仓君…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:54.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…各位  今天阳光明媚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:56.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家百忙之中  能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝仓  你被校长幽灵附身了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会贫血的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:04.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  开场白不要这么长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:11.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:22.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位  谢谢大家在我不在的这两年里照顾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:26.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够有今天的我全都是托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:29.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你也快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:37.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,严重妻管严啊  朝仓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衫并
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:50.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩了这么久了  感觉有多少都能吃得下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很好吃呢  爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:56.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  和大家一起什么都觉得好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:57.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:00.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要注意营养均衡  蔬菜也要多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:01.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝仓君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想逃避吃蔬菜吗  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:10.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是  只是去拿点肉过来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:12.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来后我会吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我陪你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:16.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:23.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  我不在的两年你一直这样为哥哥着想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大概就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他有没有耍性子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:35.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有  一点也没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:37.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也得向你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢朝仓君才这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:53.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  我也是喜欢朝仓才这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开…开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春我最喜欢音梦前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二位是香蕉  第三四…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:11.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然排名不靠前但我很喜欢朝仓前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:15.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都喜欢朝仓君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？  在说我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:24.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  正在谈论朝仓君大受欢迎的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也得参战才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:32.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝仓  我爱你  朝仓啊  亲一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:32.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:55.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:18:00.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得把这份心…收起来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱茜亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢他？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:15.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:22.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为和纯一在一起的小鸟看起来是那么幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露馅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:36.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…非常喜欢朝仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:54.60,DefaultS,,0000,0000,0000,,香波弄到眼睛里去了好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐坐这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:53.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我们交班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:56.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晒的好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:03.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:09.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:13.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为检查身体时被你看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:20.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:26.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天得补回和朝仓君的两年空白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好好看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给  拿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:47.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,满地石头真难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝仓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:58.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有重要的事情和你讲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:02.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衫并
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是梦话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SPECIAL！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…  小鸟她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经…  不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:20.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少女的眼泪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:25.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明喜欢纯一  为什么不说实话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:32.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对小鸟而言那是幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:37.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:14.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月光下波光鳞鳞的海面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:17.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在远处窃窃私语的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:20.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被夏天的气息所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:26.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻关闭了的梦之门  再次慢慢打开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:30.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心却如此平静
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:37.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满悲伤的回忆  何时才能变得幸福呢？
